snippet.title: Disney is Altering The Deal
snippet.description:
Recently Disney tried to alter the deal they had with Sony regarding Spider Man, Sony didn't approve and Spider Man in the MCU is no more :(

The internet is going crazy about this sudden news, and I too am pretty sad to see one of my favourite Marvel Cinematic Universe characters leave.

I wanted to make a little meme thing about and here it is. I hope you like it, This is from Star Wars The Empire Strikes Back.

If you like what you see, be sure to like, comment, share and subscribe!
